            <thetext>At the moment the method &quot;getCompleteHtml&quot; does only return styles for the body element and no styles for other elements.

The styles added to the editable document have to be divided into 

  - styles necessary for the editing mode
  - styles which apply to the content
  
to be able to e.g. style every &quot;P&quot; element. This style has to be provided by the &quot;getCompleteHtml&quot; method.</thetext>
